## Summary
This documentation page provides an overview of Amplitude Data, a suite of governance tools for defining, tracking, verifying, and improving data quality across the platform, including planning tools to prevent issues upfront, the Ampli developer toolkit for type-safe tracking, and data management features for enriching metadata, cleaning data, creating derived properties, and monitoring data quality in real-time.

